@startuml
title UC-004 - Session và live scan

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Super Admin\n(`SUPER_ADMIN`)" as SA
actor "Warehouse Manager\n(`WAREHOUSE_MANAGER`)" as WM
actor "Staff\n(`STAFF`)" as ST
actor "RFID Reader\nST-H103 UHF" as Reader

rectangle "RFID Tracking System" {
  usecase "UC-004\nSession và\nlive scan" as Main
  usecase "Tạo session" as CreateSession
  usecase "Gửi scanStream /\nliveScan" as SendScan
  usecase "Nhận scanDetected" as ReceiveScan
  usecase "Auto-create EPC lạ" as AutoCreate
  usecase "Assign product cho session" as AssignSessionProduct
}

WM --> Main
ST --> Main
WM --> CreateSession
ST --> CreateSession
Reader --> SendScan

Main .> CreateSession : <<include>>
Main .> SendScan : <<include>>
SendScan .> ReceiveScan : <<include>>
ReceiveScan .> AutoCreate : <<include>>
AssignSessionProduct ..> Main : <<extend>>

note bottom of CreateSession
POST /api/sessions
Trong UC-004 chi the hien
WAREHOUSE_MANAGER va STAFF
la nguoi tao session van hanh.
end note

note bottom of ReceiveScan
Moi websocket client co JWT hop le
deu join room scan:live va nhan scanDetected.
inventoryUpdate la luong rieng cua
room admin:dashboard cho role ADMIN.
end note

note bottom of AssignSessionProduct
PATCH /api/sessions/:id/assign-product
Khong thuoc flow chinh cua UC-004.
Neu can, co the mo ta o use case rieng.
end note

@enduml
